hcc_text: Westchester Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Westchester Avenue at Westchester Avenue Br, Bronx River Avenue and Close Avenue, there were 2 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
